headline: MSCI Publishes Investor Presentation
summary: NEW YORK, November 25, 2025--MSCI Inc. ("MSCI" or the "Company") (NYSE: MSCI) published an investor presentation for investors and analysts on its Investor Relations homepage, ir.msci.com, on Tuesday, November 25, 2025. The Company’s management may use this presentation during meetings with investors and analysts.
